/** 
 * Get the value of the boolean field or maybe <code>null</code>. Note that you usually want to use {@link #getValueAsBoolean()} instead of this method, as {@link #getValueAsBoolean()} considers the default valueof boolean fields. That is, boolean form fields have the value <code>false</code> if not explicitly set to something else.
 * @return the boolean value of this form field or <code>null</code> if no value was explicitly provided.
 * @see #getValueAsBoolean()
 * @since 4.4.5
 */
public Boolean getValueAsBooleanOrNull(){
  return value;
}
